name: Isdc.Ui.Dropdown

aliases.name: DropDownProperties
aliases.comment:
DropDownProperties contains all needed data and msg types for the multiCheckDropdown

    dropdownModel =
        { labelText = "Hello world"
        , dropDownValue = "Some value you determine"
        , options =
            [ { label = "Foo"
              , value = "foo"
              , checked = False
              }
            , { label = "Bar"
              , value = "bar"
              , checked = False
              }
            ]
        , open = False
        , openMessage = Open
        , toggleMessage = Toggle
        , searchMessage = Search
        , saveMessage = Save
        , cancelMessage = Cancel
        , search = ""
        }
aliases.type: { labelText : String , dropDownValue : String , options : List Isdc.Ui.Dropdown.Option , open : Bool , openMessage : msg , toggleMessage : String -> msg , searchMessage : String -> msg , saveMessage : msg , cancelMessage : msg , search : String }

values.name: multiCheckDropdown
values.comment:
multiCheckDropdown is a dropdown with checkboxes and confirmation buttons.

    -- Example usage
    dropdownModel =
        { labelText = "Hello world"
        , dropDownValue = "Some value you determine"
        , options =
        [ { label = "Foo"
        , value = "foo"
        , checked = False
        }
        , { label = "Bar"
        , value = "bar"
        , checked = False
        }
        ]
        , open = False
        , openMessage = Open
        , toggleMessage = Toggle
        , searchMessage = Search
        , saveMessage = Save
        , cancelMessage = Cancel
        , search = ""
        }
    multiCheckDropdown dropdownModel

values.name: multiCheckDropdownItem
values.comment: multiCheckDropdownItem is a single checkbox and label which can send a message to toggle the checkbox

comment:
# Typography

@docs display2, display1, headline, title, subhead1, subhead2, body2, body1, bodyCompact, caption

values.name: body1
values.comment: body1 is a medium-small sized font which has a medium weight.

values.name: body2
values.comment: body2 is a medium-small sized font which has a semi-bold weight.

values.name: bodyCompact
values.comment: body2 is a medium-small sized font which has a medium weight and small line height.

values.name: caption
values.comment: caption is a small sized font which has a medium font weight and small line height.

values.name: display1
values.comment: display2 is a style with a large font size and line height with a medium font weight. It is smaller than display.

values.name: display2
values.comment: display2 is a style with a very large font size and line height with a medium font

values.name: headline
values.comment: headline is a style with a large font size and line height with a medium font weight. It is smaller than display1.

values.name: subhead1
values.comment: subhead1 is a medium sized font which has a medium weight.

values.name: subhead2
values.comment: subhead2 is a bold medium sized font which.

values.name: title
values.comment: title is a style with a large font size and line height with a semi-bold weight. It is smaller than headline.

values.name: searchIcon
values.comment: searchIcon is an icon with an outline of a magnifying glass

values.name: loader
values.comment: loader for use in conjuction with external css
